@baseUrl = https://localhost:7115

### List Products (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?page=1&pageSize=10

### List Products with category-oriented name filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?page=1&pageSize=10&filters=name@=Electronics

### List Products with exact category name filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?page=1&pageSize=10&filters=categoryName==Books

### List Products with sorting ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?page=1&pageSize=10&sorts=price

### List Products with sorting descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?page=1&pageSize=10&sorts=-price

### List Products with filters and sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?page=2&pageSize=20&filters=name@=Sports&sorts=-price

